how can I help you, hun?

378
00:17:46,868 --> 00:17:49,604
I would like
a new look, please.

379
00:17:49,637 --> 00:17:52,339
Oh, what's giving you
the gringles,

380
00:17:52,372 --> 00:17:53,708
doll face?

381
00:17:53,741 --> 00:17:56,143
I just feel so...

382
00:17:56,911 --> 00:17:58,478
